quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  21,11,"Kaawee ko heewiri wa ca'e …óe Men halki …óum sabu too√±irgol majje keefeeru ngun, Men Tagi …ìaawo majje yim…ìe goo!"
  21,12,"Tuma nde halkanoo…ìe …ìen yi'unoo Lepte mulay…óe …óen, tawi kam…ìe hi…ìe yaccoo doga saare ma…ì…ìe nden immorde e [kulol] halkeede."
  21,13,"∆Åe noddiroyee fii jalnorgol: "Wata on dogu dey, yiltee(nduttee) faade e ko wonuno…óon e mu'un kon immorde e neemaaji e dakammeeji mo'on, e ko…óan…óe mo'on kadi; belajo'o on lannditoyte go…ó…óu e fii aduna mo'on on"."
  21,14,"∆Åee too√±oo…ìe qirritoyoo bakkatuuji ma…ì…ìe …óin …ìe wi'a: "Eeyoo, halakuyee amen e hayrere amen, pellet, menen men woniino too√±u…ìe sabu yeddugol amen Alla"."
  21,15,"Seerataa qirritagol ma…ì…ìe bakkatuuji ma…ì…ìe …óin e noddugol ma…ì…ìe e wonkiiji ma…ì…ìe …óin halakuyee, noddaandu ma…ì…ìe ndu …ìe fillitotoo ndun haa Men wa…óa …ìe yeru remuru so√±aandu, ko …ìe maayu…ìe dillugol alanaa …ìe."
  21,16,"Men tagiraali kammu ngun e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji fijindaaru e puyndan, ko woni, Men tagirii…ói fii tinndinor…ói e Kattan…óe Amen."
  21,17,"Sinndo Men faalano jogitaade sonnaajo maa…óum …ìi…ó…óo Men jogitotono …óum ko woni kon ka Amen, Men wonaali non wa…óoo…ìe …óum sabu Senagol Amen e …óum."
  21,18,"Ko woni Me…óen werloo Goonga ka Men wahayini kan faade e Nulaa…ìe Amen …ìen e dow meere yim…ìe geddi …ìen ka fuyna nde, tawa meere ma…ì…ìe nden ko yahunde iwi fes, no woodani on -onon wi'u…ìe …ìen hiMo jogitii sonnaajo e …ìi…ó…óo- halkaare sabu ko sifi…óon Mo kon ko O hanndaa e mu'un."
  21,19,"Ko Kanko Tun woodani O Senike laamu kammuu- li …óin e Laamu leydi ndin, …ìen wom…ìe ka Makko kadi immorde e Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen …ìe mawnikin- taaka Dewal Makko ngal, …ìe tampirtaa ngal."
  21,20,"Hi…ìe duumii e Subhinanagol Alla e duumaade, …ìe haa…ìataa e …óum."
  21,21,"Ko woni, sirkoo…ìe …ìen jogiti rewetee…ói gaanin Alla, …ói wuurtintaa may…ìe …ìen, ko honno …ìe rewirta ronku…óo gaayi …óum?!"
  21,22,"Si tawiino laatino ka kammuuli e ka leydi rewetee…ói …óuu…óu…ói …ói …ói…ói-kala …ói bonirayno poo…óondiral rewetee…ìe …ìen ka laamu, ko selli kon no lunndii …óum, Alla Jom Arsi kin O Senike gaayi ko sirko…ìe …ìen sifotoo Mo kon fenaande wonndema no woodani Mo kafidaa…ìe."
  21,23,"Alla ko Kanko woni teel…óo e Laamu Makko ngun e √ëaawoore Makko nden, hay e gooto lanndotaako Mo fii ko O hoddir kon e ko O √ëaawi kon, Kanko le O lanndoyto jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen gaayi golle ma…ì…ìe …óen, O yo…ìa …ìe e dow …óum."
  21,24,"Ko woni, …ìe jogiti gaanin Alla rewetee…ói, maakan an Nulaa…óo- …ìee sirkoo…ìe: "Addee hujja mon on e hanndugol rewugol …ói, awa ndee Deftere jippinaa- nde e am, e Defte jippinaa…óe …óen e Nulaa…ìe …ìen on maraa hujja e nder majje, ko woni, …ìur…ìe …ìen e sirkoo…ìe …ìen …ìe tuugutaako si wanaa e majjere e √±emmbugol, hara kam…ìe ko …ìe …óurnii…ìe e ja…ìugol Goonga kan."